A couple celebrating their one-year anniversary finds that their relationship is more fragile than either had anticipated in this drama from director Jon FitzGerald. Committed couple Collin and Hugh have pledged their lives to one another, but as Hugh begins planning a party to celebrate their first year of commitment it soon becomes obvious that Collin is having second thoughts about their relationship. ~ Jason Buchanan, All Movie Guide
